fields.title: Jaguar E Type
fields.description: The Jaguar E Type has been voted the best car ever built, even Enzo Ferrari said that it was \"the most beautiful car he had ever seen.\" Surprisingly easy to drive and an absolutely perfect cruiser, any time of year. Presented in a beautiful Claret Red, our E type has been fully re built from the chassis up. The interior is a beautiful place to sit and it is even fitted with a retro radio capable of playing mp3's.     Hiring our Jaguar E type couldn’t be simpler, we include all insurance and give you a lesson on how to drive her competently and how to operate all the controls and put the roof up! The E type is available for self drive hire and for weddings. She is also available for magazine shoots, media publications and corporate events.

fields.title: Mercedes 190 sl
fields.description: Our Mercedes 190 SL is available for self drive hire and proves one of our most popular cars to rent especially for weddings. For your special occasion, we can provide a bespoke car transportation service which can include the delivery of this vehicle to your chosen start location and collection from the same address or different address if needed.

fields.title: Aston Martin Oscar India V8
fields.description: Our stunning Aston Martin Oscar India for self drive hire. Be Bond for a day, or a week! Our new addition to the fleet is our elegant Aston Martin Oscar India V8 available for self drive hire.      The two rear seats can accommodate children easily or adults on shorter journeys if need be! Available for self drive hire, weddings, corporate events, birthday surprises and any other special occasion you can think of. She is also available for all media work such as photoshoots, magazine shoots, film, TV and Road trips.

fields.title: Austin Healy 3000
fields.description:
One of the most recognisable British cars ever made. With its two tone period perfect colouring, our Austin Healey 3000 is one of the most iconic cars of our fleet. Available to hire with a hood if the weather is against you. Our Austin Healey has 4 seats so it is great for that extra bit of flexibility. The powerful straight six 3 litre engine sounds absolutely amazing burbling from the size exhausts (seen under the passenger door.) She is a sports car thoroughbred and looks and sounds every bit the part. 

​

fields.title: Rolls Royce Silver Cloud 3
fields.description: Our Rolls Royce Silver Cloud 3 is another exquisitely kept piece of automotive history. The two tone paintwork perfectly complements the grey leather and red interior. Feel extra special arriving in true vintage style. This car is also available to rent to drive yourself! If you don't fancy wafting around behind the wheel, why not allow for us to supply a chauffeured as an option.

fields.title: Porsche 911T
fields.description: We are very excited to have this join the fleet this year! This is a 1970 D series Porsche 911T with a 2.2 litre air cooled twin Webber carbureted flat 6 mated to a five speed 901 dogleg gearbox. We are very excited to have this join the fleet this year! This is a 1970 D series Porsche 911T with a 2.2 litre air cooled twin Webber carbureted flat 6 mated to a five speed 901 dogleg gearbox.

fields.title: DeLorean DMC-12
fields.description: Our DeLorean DMC-12 is our wild card modern classic car that we are proud to offer for self drive hire. Completely original in both concept and design, the Delorean turns heads wherever she goes. The car features gull-wing doors and an innovative fibre glass body structure with a steel backbone chassis - hugely ahead of its "time." She has a growling V6 sitting behind the seats and manual transmission for an ultimate driving experience.

fields.title: Aston Martin DB7
fields.description: Our stunning Aston Martin DB7 is a new addition to the fleet in 2017 and is available for self drive hire. Be Bond for a day, or a long weekend. She is in the original flawless Grampian Green and is the epitome of a true modern British supercar. The interior is a beautiful and comfortable place to sit with two tone green and cream leather seats.

fields.title: Fiat 500L
fields.description: Now you can rent another legendary classic car form our fleet - the Fiat 500! In great condition with bright shiny yellow paint and the option to open up the roof to let the sun shine in! She is a right hand drive so that makes it a little less daunting on the road. Being easy to drive even for people of over 6 foot (tested by our in house 6"3 Mark Webb!) once you get to grips with the size, she is happy on A and B roads cruising at 40 or 50mph with no real effort. Perfect for weddings, birthdays and TV appearances, this piece of Italian history brings joy to all that see and drive her.

fields.title: Morris Minor Million
fields.description: Another beautiful addition to our fleet is the classic Morris Minor Million. It has a perfectly contrasting interior and just oozes vintage chic.  Being easy to drive she brings smiles at every turn. Absolutely perfect for vintage weddings and reliving the past. Available for self drive hire, weddings, corporate events, birthday surprises and any other special occasion you can think of. She is also available for all media work such as photoshoots, magazine shoots, film, TV and Road trips.

fields.title: Triumph Herald 12/50
fields.description: The Triumph Herald made its debut in 1959. Soon becoming one of the most popular family vehicles around. "We used to have one of those" is what we hear a lot at Webb's. The 12/50 (fitted with a 13/60 engine) developed 61bhp (hence the 60) and our example for hire is in fresh White paint and is excellent fun as a convertible. Great fun to drive and be driven in!

fields.title: Austin Mini
fields.description: Our Austin Mini is just about as much fun as you can have with a 1 Litre engine! With a great retro interior, you can enjoy zipping about in style in our lovely budget classic car. She has a period Blaupunkt stereo, wind up windows and just about room for 5 people!  On the road, the Mini is easy to drive and surprisingly quick and nimble which is sure to make you smile every time. The beautiful cream paint and small wheels give the Mini a neat retro look and would be a great groom's car wedding car, prom car or special treat fun car!

fields.title: MG B Roadster
fields.description: Our perfect blue MG B is a great car for lazy summer drives or long autumn sunsets. A great cruiser as well as a fun, sporty A-road car with overdrive for the motorway. The MG B is a perfect choice for those looking for something familiar. The best all rounder of our fleet. Not to say our MG B is a cheap classic car to rent but it is our most reasonably priced car in our fleet. However it is our best kept example and defies its half century age! The interior is immaculate with newly covered leathers seats and an unmarked bodywork with contrasting chrome. She pulls through the 4 speed box very smoothly and is a true joy to drive. With the elegant period steering wheel, cornering and parking her is a breeze. The roof is quick and easy to put up - a true 'no fuss' classic car with bags of attitude.

fields.title: Alfa Romeo Spider 2000
fields.description: This Alfa Romeo Spider was produced from 1966 to 1993 and is a real design classic. It remained in production for almost three decades!  The 2000 cars were modified in 1974 and 1975 respectively to include two small seats behind the front seats, becoming a 2+2 such as this example.

fields.title: Land Rover Series 1
fields.description:
We are very fond of our trusty Land Rover Series 1 - she is always ready to work and loves moving people around. If you are looking for an alternative wedding car or brides maids vehicle, the Landy seats up to 7 people. The roof can be completely removed creating a great fun convertible option. Ideal for a weekend jaunt to the New Forest, a quirky prom car or an ideal extra in films.  ​For your special occasion, we can provide a bespoke car transportation service which can include the delivery of this vehicle to your chosen start location. We also offer collection from the same address or a different address if you need.

​

fields.title: Porsche 356 Speedster
fields.description: Our amazing 356 Speedster Pilgrim Continuation runs on the same flat 4 air cooled engine, running gear and dimensions as the original to create a truly authentic experience. Easy to drive, ​4 speed box with a great roof for if the weather closes in.

fields.title: Ac Cobra Continuation
fields.description: We are so exited to announce our fiendishly good new addition to the fleet - The AC Cobra Pilgrim Continuation. She benefits from having an automatic gearbox which perfectly complements the 350 V8 5.76 litre engine. With 340hp - she is no slouch and makes the most glorious sound. On the road, she is very easy to drive, the steering is light and responsive, the brakes are very good and as comparable to a brand new car to help scrub the speed off when needed and she is very comfortable on the motorway as well as windy A and B roads. Being 6ft '3 tall, I wondered if I would fit comfortably but there is plenty of space in the cabin for even the most proportionately challenged of people and is a very comfortable place to be.

fields.title: MG A Roadster
fields.description:
Our bright red MG A is a shining example of a classic British roadster. With the roof down and the sound of the engine burbling in the background, you can’t get any closer to the essence of classic motoring. Our personal favourite, we feel the MG A strikes a perfect balance between practicality, style and pure driving pleasure. Her timeless lines seem photograph well from any angle and the perfect red paintwork complements almost any event. 

​
